    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter! This car is in fair condition and offers a solid foundation for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver with character. While it shows some signs of its journey, it still has plenty of life left and drives with heart. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a great value and a car that gets the job done!",
